{"tid":589331,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"以為自己唔會對個水泡動情","createTime":"2018-03-11T21:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T20:12:06.000Z","uid":174592,"like":18,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b828526c12679b8c4f24375d5f20bc46e82927de","tid":589331,"uid":174592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T21:54:21.000Z","msg":"我個水泡同我原本個女朋友好fd,兩個真係兩姊妹咁。但係我原本個女朋友好乖女，而個水泡就比較淫底。<br />\n咁幾個月前同我女朋友鬧大交，佢頂我唔順，話我成日唔信佢佢好大壓力，原本我都以為有得掹，但係佢同我個水泡傾完之後就好決絕，死都唔肯一齊返，要做朋友。咁我都keep住有同佢傾計，但佢真係唔再當我係男朋友。<br />\n接住落黎個一個月我都好絕望，日日都好唔開心，想喊都喊唔出，好彩水泡係接下黎個個月成日陪我傾計，又同我出街周圍去。我先冇咁寂寞。過左冇耐我同個水泡一齊左。但直到個陣，我都仲係好掛住之前個個。對個水泡一d感情都冇。有時同佢出街都會覺得有d煩。<br />\n但自從上個禮拜同佢扑完之後，我就慢慢對以前個個唔上心。越黎越愛個水泡。終於到而家我進入比人撚狗既狀態。佢成日都話我地好對唔住我舊女朋友，跟住就若即若離咁，搞到我個心仲痛過之前。<br />\n點解我唔愛你個陣你就痴撚住哂，搞到有次我差d想打撚柒你，但我愛你愛到入骨時你就要撚返我狗？女人真係好賤格，全部都只係沙包，肉便器，家務機。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0db97b414a6a9d8811d42113f4a7699c477f89","tid":589331,"uid":20428,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T21:56:27.000Z","msg":"佢嫌你下面廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175f4e8d7ce7bc42a87196604bd74ec12ad5b95d","tid":589331,"uid":174592,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec0db97b414a6a9d8811d42113f4a7699c477f89","tid":589331,"uid":20428,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T21:56:27.000Z","msg":"佢嫌你下面廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T21:57:21.000Z","msg":"冇可能，直到而家我地都keep住有扑野，但係佢就乜都唔想講，我覺得自己好似做鴨咁"},{"pid":"f43ec4c4a693415699c97d3597c1065a38604d41","tid":589331,"uid":174592,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T22:00:00.000Z","msg":"好想打女人了，打到d m血係個鼻度流出黎"},{"pid":"098ef1d2967276923fff4c0f94ef8cb3dd434e83","tid":589331,"uid":103887,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T23:07:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c5f995066dbae33e9a7145ef08352a97d6a815b","tid":589331,"uid":52566,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f43ec4c4a693415699c97d3597c1065a38604d41","tid":589331,"uid":174592,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T22:00:00.000Z","msg":"好想打女人了，打到d m血係個鼻度流出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:09:00.000Z","msg":"勁牙清<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70028da0b45a2c7f9555eabe2d338b47e86917b7","tid":589331,"uid":138138,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:40:14.000Z","msg":"事實證明 男人下半身思考係真既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30d339263fa00a6ba95e68834eb68dfd5c2c8d1","tid":589331,"uid":174592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70028da0b45a2c7f9555eabe2d338b47e86917b7","tid":589331,"uid":138138,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:40:14.000Z","msg":"事實證明 男人下半身思考係真既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:59:26.000Z","msg":"我真係好愛佢⋯"},{"pid":"003b9c9306005acdbf84502a66d320d445102d9f","tid":589331,"uid":175004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:03:42.000Z","msg":"唔吊可能沒事 一打通左就淡了"},{"pid":"707f4e44f883357aa459ce9acba79c5126cd4305","tid":589331,"uid":174592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"003b9c9306005acdbf84502a66d3